tion\": {\n      \"description\": \"The city and state, e.g. San Francisco, CA\",\n      \"type\": \"string\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"required\": [\n    \"location\"\n  ],\n  \"type\": \"object\"\n}\n```\n\nYou are a helpful assistant.",
